data.description: Welcome to this ideal single-family home, tailor-made for a contractor or a handy buyer with a passion for renovation. With the perfect blend of potential and location, this home is situated on an acre of land, zoned R1-40, in the highly coveted area of Yorktown.    This ranch-style home offers the convenience of one-level living, making it accessible and accommodating for all. Boasting 4 bedrooms, 3.5 baths, and a generous 2766 sq ft of space, this residence is ideally suited for both living and working purposes. The layout provides ample room for customization, allowing you to create the perfect space to suit your unique needs.    While this home requires some love and attention, its well-designed floor plan and spacious dimensions provide an excellent foundation for your vision. Unleash your creativity and transform this property into the home of your dreams.    A standout feature of this property is the expansive, level backyard. With abundant space for outdoor activities and entertaining guests, this area is a true haven. Whether you envision hosting memorable summer gatherings or simply enjoying quiet moments in nature, this backyard offers endless possibilities.    Furthermore, this property boasts a sizable parking area, providing ample room for multiple vehicles. This convenience is particularly valuable for those with a busy lifestyle or for homeowners who love to entertain and host gatherings.    The location of this home is second to none. Situated close to Route 6 and Taconic, you'll enjoy easy access to nearby towns, shops, and restaurants. This prime location ensures that everything you need is just moments away.    While this home requires some TLC, its exceptional location, spacious layout, and potential for customization make it a truly remarkable investment opportunity. Don't miss your chance to breathe new life into this property and create a space that perfectly reflects your style and preferences. Schedule a showing today and uncover the limitless potential that awaits you in this highly desirable Yorktown home.
